    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six. This specimen is mechanically flawless, boasting a high-pressure VANOS system that has been fully overhauled and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise, tactile engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential that remains tight. The naturally aspirated power plant pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline with no rod bearing concerns. Finished in Carbon Black, the paint depth and clarity are exceptional, and the underside is free of any fluid seepage or oxidation. A purist\u2019s example with zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
